00:08.008 --> 00:11.612 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: On the "NewsHour"
tonight:
President-elect Trump taps
ExxonMobil executive

00:11.645 --> 00:17.818 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Rex Tillerson for secretary of
state, raising
concerns even among Republicans
about the

00:17.851 --> 00:20.053 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
