concerns about
the planned nomination.

03:06.219 --> 03:11.525 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There's also word that another
Texan, former
Governor Rick Perry, could be
tapped to be

03:11.558 --> 03:13.660 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
energy secretary.

03:13.693 --> 03:16.930 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But the transition at Energy
could be rocky.

03:16.963 --> 03:22.302 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The department said today that
it will not
provide the names of employees
who've worked

03:22.335 --> 03:27.007 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
on climate change, as the Trump
transition
team requested.

03:27.040 --> 03:34.181 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There are also reports that
Montana Congressman
Ryan Zinke could be tapped for
interior secretary.

03:34.214 --> 03:39.486 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Meanwhile, President Obama
criticized Mr.
Trump's lack of interest in
receiving a daily

03:39.519 --> 03:41.254 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
intelligence briefing.

03:41.288 --> 03:43.090 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He spoke last night on "The
Daily Show."

03:43.123 --> 03:45.892 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA, President of the
United States:
It doesn't matter how smart you
are.

03:45.926 --> 03:51.731 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You have to have the best
information possible
to make the best decisions
possible.

03:51.765 --> 04:03.009 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And if you're not getting their
perspective,
their detailed perspective, then
you are flying

04:03.043 --> 04:04.911 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
blind.

04:04.945 --> 04:08.448 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Back at Trump
Tower today,
the president-elect met with
Microsoft billionaire

04:08.482 --> 04:10.016 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Bill Gates.

04:10.050 --> 04:12.252 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BILL GATES, Founder, Microsoft:
We had a good
conversation about innovation.

04:12.285 --> 04:18.592 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Others he met
with, pro football
greats Jim Brown and Ray Lewis
and entertainer

04:18.625 --> 04:20.427 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Kanye West.

04:20.460 --> 04:25.165 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Tonight, Mr. Trump is making the
latest stop
on what he's calling his thank
you tour, this

04:25.198 --> 04:26.967 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
time in Wisconsin.

04:27.000 --> 04:30.737 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
