effects of hydraulic
fracturing, or fracking, on
drinking water.

04:36.309 --> 04:41.214 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
It found the oil and gas
drilling technique
can contaminate underground
water in some

04:41.248 --> 04:42.749 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
cases.

04:42.782 --> 04:45.585 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It also said there is not
evidence to estimate
the severity of the risk.

04:45.619 --> 04:50.390 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The report dropped an earlier
finding that
fracking has not caused
widespread systemic

04:50.423 --> 04:52.259 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
harm to water supplies.

04:52.292 --> 04:57.697 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Ohio's Republican
Governor
John Kasich has vetoed a closely
watched anti-abortion

04:57.731 --> 04:59.533 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
bill.

04:59.566 --> 05:04.137 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
