separate bill
banning abortion after 20 weeks
of pregnancy.

05:14.381 --> 05:16.917 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Seventeen states already have
similar laws.

05:16.950 --> 05:21.655 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: President
Obama today signed
a sweeping law, including new
spending on

05:21.688 --> 05:23.790 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
cancer research and drug abuse.

05:23.823 --> 05:27.928 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
