aims to challenge
President Vladimir Putin, who is
expected

06:11.538 --> 06:13.340 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to seek a fourth term.

06:13.373 --> 06:19.212 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
