for fraud in
a case that he says is
politically motivated.

06:19.246 --> 06:21.281 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If he is convicted, he would be
barred from
running.

06:21.314 --> 06:25.752 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: A railway
strike across
Southern England today caused
the worst railway

06:25.785 --> 06:27.554 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
disruption there in 20 years.

06:27.587 --> 06:32.659 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It is part of a longstanding
dispute over
whether train drivers or
on-board guards should

06:32.692 --> 06:34.461 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
