but union officials
defended their stance.

06:43.536 --> 06:45.238 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MAN: It's a safety issue.

06:45.272 --> 06:49.409 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The reality for us is that the
increasing
level of trains, the increasing
amount of

06:49.442 --> 06:54.848 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
