lends itself
to a one-man operation.

06:57.651 --> 07:00.687 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The government
blamed the
unions for the impasse.

07:00.720 --> 07:03.423 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The railway owner announced new
talks for
tomorrow.

07:03.456 --> 07:06.226 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Another day,
another rally
on Wall Street.

07:06.259 --> 07:13.733 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
