family said she
always shaves about a decade off
her age.

07:33.420 --> 07:37.557 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Either way, people at her
nursing home gave
her balloons and sang happy
birthday.

07:37.590 --> 07:40.226 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And I think she
