07:42.162 --> 07:44.331 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Still to come
on the "NewsHour":
how Exxon's CEO could shape
foreign policy

07:44.364 --> 07:50.637 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
