where Tillerson
is a member of the board of
trustees.

08:40.720 --> 08:45.725 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Hamre served as deputy secretary
of defense
during the Clinton
administration.

08:45.759 --> 08:50.597 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
